Greater Trochanteric Fracture with Lesser Trochanter Extension: A Report of 2 
Cases and CT-Based Finite Element Analysis.

Yukata K(1)(2), Uchiyama Y(3), Nishida N(2), Ohgi J(3), Sakai T(2), Fujii H(1).

Author information:
(1)Department of Orthopaedic Surgery, Ogori Daiichi General Hospital, Yamaguchi, 
